org.springframework.boot.actuate.endpoint.annotation

接口 AnnotationEndpointDiscoverer.EndpointOperationFactory<T extends Operation>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the Operation type
    封闭类:
    AnnotationEndpointDiscoverer<T extends Operation,K>
    函数接口:
    这是一个函数接口, 因此可用作 lambda 表达式或方法引用的赋值目标。

    @FunctionalInterface
protected static interface AnnotationEndpointDiscoverer.EndpointOperationFactory<T extends Operation>
    An EndpointOperationFactory creates an Operation for an operation on an endpoint.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      T createOperation(String endpointId, org.springframework.core.annotation.AnnotationAttributes operationAttributes, Object target, Method operationMethod, OperationType operationType, long timeToLive)
      Creates an EndpointOperation for an operation on an endpoint.

    • 方法详细资料

      • createOperation

        T createOperation(String endpointId,
                  org.springframework.core.annotation.AnnotationAttributes operationAttributes,
                  Object target,
                  Method operationMethod,
                  OperationType operationType,
                  long timeToLive)
        Creates an EndpointOperation for an operation on an endpoint.
        参数:
        endpointId - the id of the endpoint
        operationAttributes - the annotation attributes for the operation
        target - the target that implements the operation
        operationMethod - the method on the bean that implements the operation
        operationType - the type of the operation
        timeToLive - the caching period in milliseconds
        返回:
        the operation info that describes the operation
